---
description: Enforces whitespace rules to maintain code quality and consistency.
alwaysApply: true
---
- No Trailing Whitespace: Never add trailing whitespace on any line. Always check before saving files.
- Consistent Indentation: Use 2 spaces for indentation (no tabs).
- Single Newline at EOF: End all files with exactly one newline character.
- No Multiple Blank Lines: Maximum one consecutive blank line allowed.
